Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:02:02.43,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}背負「自由之翼」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.35,0:02:09.57,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}緊握決意抵在左胸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:14.36,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}劈裂「愚行之螺旋」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:17.91,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}翱翔於蒼穹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:23.25,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}自由之翼
