Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.08,0:21:54.34,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs48\fad(300,300)\blur3}如果我不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.34,0:21:59.30,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs48\fad(300,300)\blur3}你還能夠說是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.30,0:22:04.60,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs48\fad(300,300)\blur3}崩壞的砂器散落一地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.72,0:22:09.94,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs48\fad(300,300)\blur3}破碎的心能否重新拾起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.94,0:22:19.07,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs48\fad(300,300)\blur3}何人的呼喚 幻化為耳鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.07,0:22:24.04,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs48\fad(300,300)\blur3}時間似乎靜止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.16,0:22:27.08,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs48\fad(300,300)\blur3}啊 覺醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.08,0:22:32.00,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}衝破這無邊的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.25,0:22:37.13,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}疾風一般逃離
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.51,0:22:42.10,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}曾如行屍走肉一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.10,0:22:49.10,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}我們 到城牆之外 再相見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.10,0:22:53.44,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}在地圖之外
